{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/LDGIF1_Lore.gif?t=1728030565\" />Uncover the past as you explore a top down open world filled with puzzles and action-packed boss fights. Defeat enemies in a real-time strategy battle system. All brought to life with traditional, frame by frame, hand-drawn animation. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/1ADVENTURE_EN.png?t=1728030565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/LDGIF2_Explore.gif?t=1728030565\" />Explore a world filled with puzzles, using tile-based movement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manipulate buttons, cannons, or even cows. View your environment as your personal playground, and discover how different combinations can lead to your success. Drive different vehicles to enhance mobility and abilities. Memorize different objects' behaviors to help you react quickly during action-oriented puzzles. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/2FIGHT_EN.png?t=1728030565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/LDGIF3_Combat.gif?t=1728030565\" />Engage in combat through a strategic tile-sliding puzzle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thoughtfully coordinate your tile placement to defend against enemy attacks and create opportunities for dealing damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each character possesses a unique three-tile combo, executing these in sequence will result in enhanced damage, at a higher risk of counterattacks. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/3BOSSES_EN